videos.headline: Bowling Green's Gregory stops Eastern Michigan with pick
videos.description: Eastern Michigan's Brogan Roback's pass is intercepted by Bowling Green's Montre Gregory for an 18-yard return to set up the Falcons.

videos.headline: Cleveland races for 72-yard TD
videos.description: Josh Cleveland runs 72 yards for a touchdown to put Bowling Green on top 7-0 in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Roback connects with Bailey for TD
videos.description: Eastern Michigan's Brogan Roback hits Sergio Bailey for a 18-yard touchdown to tie the game 7-7 in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Doege TD run reclaims the lead for Bowling Green
videos.description: Quarterback Jarret Doege rushes from 2 yards out for a Falcons touchdown to reclaim the lead 17-13 in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Eastern Michigan with a big play on D
videos.description: Juan Giraldo's interception of Bowling Green's Jarret Doege stops the Falcons drive.

videos.headline: Eriksen bulls in for TD for Eastern Michigan
videos.description: Ian Eriksen bulldozers in for a 1-yard touchdown run to reclaim the lead for the Eagles.

videos.headline: Eriksen rumbles for second TD for Eastern Michigan
videos.description: Ian Eriksen's second touchdown run adds to the lead for Eastern Michigan in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Bowling Green's Redding makes leaping TD catch
videos.description: Teo Redding high points the ball for a 20-yard touchdown catch to close the gap for the Falcons.

videos.headline: Doege to Guyton gives Bowling Green the lead
videos.description: Jarret Doege hits Datrin Guyton for a 62-yard touchdown pass to give the Falcons the lead in the third quarter.
